\par }{\fs22 
\par Hag Eye
\par }{\fs20 A }{\i\fs20 hag eye }{\fs20 is a magic gem created by a covey. It appears to be nothing more than a semiprecious stone, but a }{\i\fs20 gem of seeing }{\fs20 or other such effect reveals it as a disembodied eye. Often, a }{\i\fs20 hag eye }{\fs20 
