\par A summoned invisible stalker undertakes whatever task the summoner commands, even if the task sends it hundreds or thousands of miles away. The creature follows a command until the task is completed and obeys only the summoner. However, it resents protrac
ted missions or complex tasks and seeks to pervert its instructions accordingly.
